snippet.title: Hunger Games Simulator [HUNGER GAMES EDITION]
snippet.description:
Uhhhhh yeah, this is an April fools video

If you enjoy this hunger games simulator video, make sure to check out my playlist of other videos. Trust me, my other ones are better lol, this one has no editing or music or anything. My other ones are better made, so if this is somehow the first video of mine you’re seeing, please give me another chance 😅. https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLyKtHQta-a8ME3INImOuMCeY9esUiRAXr&si=lhXcyVMQ_EBbI8NE
